						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">I read somewhere that most changes you do to the ppu only become visible in the next scanline. Is that true? If it is it's, the "fraction of cycle" thing is not such a big problem, right?</div>
