					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You don't have to get a so complicated stuff.
<br />Just use a sprite 0 hit, if it has it's bottom bit set, and if it's well down, you won't see it. If the water position goes below a point of the screen, you can simply disable it and don't wait for a sprite 0 hit, so you have enough timimg for game logic. I remember a megaman stage that have cool tricks with water, but I forget exactly where.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Life is complex: it has both real and imaginary components.</div>
